<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>Generators are designed to make it easier to customize the <code>sails new</code> and <code>sails generate</code> command-line tools, and provide better support for different Gruntfiles, configuration options, view engines, coffeescript, etc.</p>
<h4 id="structure" permalink="structure">Structure</h4>
<p>A generator has:</p>
<p>(1) a dictionary of build directives called <code>targets</code></p>
<p>(2) a <code>templatesDirectory</code>, which is an absolute path to the folder of templates to use in <code>targets</code></p>
<p>(3) optionally a <code>before</code> function and an <code>after</code> function (async logic which is run before and after respectively).</p>
